      "content": "he's really stubborn about it though. he says his face feels fine and he's not having any actual pain, just that weird heaviness. he's insisting it's just jet lag and wants to sleep it off. you sure it can't just be the travel stress or maybe just some dehydration from the flight? it seems a bit extreme to rush to the hospital for just some tingling.",
